<taxonomicName id="5055EC81F9F14C4A4648A080E1C20382" authority="Kriebel, 2016" authorityName="Kriebel" authorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Conostegia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Conostegia procera" order="Myrtales" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="procera">Conostegia procera</taxonomicName>
(Swartz) D. Don ex DC., Prodr. 3: 174. 1828. 
<taxonomicName id="BDADDFA8E8A8ED1B94E853586917AC1B" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Melastoma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Melastoma procera" order="Myrtales" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="procera">Melastoma procera</taxonomicName>
Swartz, Prodr. Veg. Ind. Occ. 68. 1788. Type Jamaica. no date, O. Swartz s.n. (lectotype: S!, designated here; isolectotype: BM!).
</paragraph>
